first_line = "CHAPTER I\n"
last_line = "End of the Project Gutenberg EBook of War and Peace, by Leo Tolstoy\n"

fp = open('2600-0.txt')
for line in fp:
    if line == first_line:
        break

count = 0
for line in fp:
    if line == last_line:
        print(line)
        break
    count += len(line.split())
